---
// How It Works component explaining the platform workflow
---

<section class="py-24 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        How Fairmind Works
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        A comprehensive 5-step process to ensure your AI systems are fair, transparent, and compliant
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Process Steps -->
    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Connection Line -->
      <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-1/2 left-0 right-0 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-200 via-purple-200 to-green-200 transform -translate-y-1/2"></div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-8 lg:gap-4">
        
        <!-- Step 1: Data Upload -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 text-center lg:text-left">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-6">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Upload & Validate</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Upload your datasets and models. Our system automatically validates data quality, structure, and identifies potential bias sources.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Data quality assessment</li>
              <li>• Schema validation</li>
              <li>• Bias source identification</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2: Bias Analysis -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 text-center lg:text-left">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-6">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Bias Detection</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Comprehensive bias analysis using statistical methods, custom rules, and LLM-powered insights to identify fairness issues.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Statistical parity analysis</li>
              <li>• Custom fairness rules</li>
              <li>• LLM-powered insights</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3: Explainability -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 text-center lg:text-left">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-6">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Explainability</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Generate transparent explanations using SHAP, DALEX, and LIME to understand model decisions and feature importance.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• SHAP analysis</li>
              <li>• DALEX explanations</li>
              <li>• Feature importance</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4: Simulation -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 text-center lg:text-left">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-6">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">4</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Simulation & Testing</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Run bias simulations to test different scenarios, demographic shifts, and deployment impacts before going live.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Scenario modeling</li>
              <li>• Impact assessment</li>
              <li>• Risk mitigation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 5: Monitoring -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 text-center lg:text-left">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-6">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">5</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Monitor & Maintain</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Continuous monitoring with real-time alerts, performance tracking, and automated compliance reporting.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Real-time monitoring</li>
              <li>• Automated alerts</li>
              <li>• Compliance reports</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <div class="text-center mt-16">
      <a href="/demo" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200">
        Start Your Journey
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
